Definition: The location (archive) at which the data in a data collection is to be deposited.
A URL or weblink that provides the location of relevant tools or pages to a data collection. Commonly used to link to landing page that allows for downloading data contained in collection.
A license that is applied to the data in a data collection.
Organization that is funding the grant
Organization that is receiving funding from the grant
A URL or weblink that contains the text for a license.
A contributor to a project. This is often given as a list.
The funding source for a project.
A link to relevant tools/pages of a project.
A publication associated with a project.
The data collections that are part of a project.
